window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A legendary serial killer stalks the streets of a fantastical city in </b><b><i>The Helm of Midnight</i></b><b>, the stunning first novel in a new trilogy from acclaimed author Marina Lostetter.</b></p> <p>In a daring and deadly heist, thieves have made away with an artifact of terrible power - the death mask of Louis Charbon. Made by a master craftsman, it is imbued with the spirit of a monster from history, a serial murderer who terrorized the city.</p> <p>Now Charbon is loose once more, killing from beyond the grave. But these murders are different from before, not simply random but the work of a deliberate mind probing for answers to a sinister question.</p> <p>It is up to Krona Hirvath and her fellow Regulators to enter the mind of madness to stop this insatiable killer while facing the terrible truths left in his wake. </p> <p><b>A Macmillan Audio production from Tor Books</b></p>"; 
